products.title: Bella Primrose Roman Blind

Using a cotton blend fabric with delicate embroidery in fresh yellow and green tones, the bella primrose roman blind is an uplifting option that is bursting with charm and will suit a traditionally inspired interior. Product id: db-rom1052 fabric colour: primrose material: 52% polyester 48% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining headrail: durable white headrail with top or face fix brackets.
